#+TITLE: Emacs Tips and Tricks

* Emacs Tips and Tricks
  Grouped by functions

*** Helm
     M-x customize-group RET helm-faces RET


*** ERC
    https://www.emacswiki.org/emacs/ErcCommands


*** ace-jump-mode
    M-j to jump mode


*** org-mode and todos
    C-c a t     (org-todo-list)


*** Magit
    C-c g


*** Editing



*** Movement
    M-f next word
    M-b previous word
    C-a beginning of line
    C-e end of line
    C-k delete line (starting from cursor)
    C-d delete next character after the curso
    C-y   restore (yank) line
    C-x i   insert (file)
    M-<   top of file
    M->   bottom of file
    C-v   next screen
    M-v   previous screen
    C-s   search
    M-x   and then type "goto-line"
    C-x C-s   save file
    C-x C-c   quit emacs
    C-z   suspend emacs (fg to restore)
    C-x C-w	save file to different name
